snippet.textDisplay:
every Slipknot video tells a story of some kind. this story harks back to something Corey said about the making of this album...its not so much for the fans as it is for Slipknot themselves. this video is just them, doing what they do best, playing their music. its kinda dull, its pretty drab and the colorful lighting isnt something youd expect from them yet somehow it works...kinda...almost. the Silent Hill monster is a nice touch but they all just...kinda...look at it like "hmmm...yes...this monster is made of nightmares" and its a little boring.


Assassins Creed Sid is fucking cool though. that mask...*shudders* haunting
